VALUES ('RDC-RAP-PAS-UK-001', 'room-acoustic-performance', 'RT60', 'UK', 'NDV/AUT', 'jurisdiction_value', NULL, NULL, 'PAS 6463:2022 §10 Acoustics provides qualitative guidance, no quantified RT60 target for neurodivergent populations.', 'REF-00568', '§10 Acoustics and noise management, p.51-57; Table 2 Recommended room acoustic values, p.54', NULL, 'NOT-FOUND', '2026-05-18 06:00', 'session_2026-05-17-pilot-pass-3-batch-1', 1, 'Verification ATTEMPTED but content beyond fetcher token budget. Fetched PDF returned pp. i-50 only; §10 starts at p.51 and Table 2 at p.54. PAS 6463 is open-access (BSI free PDF via housinglin.org.uk) so not strictly PAYWALL, but the fetcher truncated before reaching cited section. paywall_purchase_candidate=1 flag used as a routing signal that this row needs re-verification with a higher-budget fetch or per-section direct read. Pilot doc claim of "qualitative; no numeric comparator" is plausible given PAS 6463 Foreword self-describes as guidance/recommendations not specification, but NOT verified at the section level. NOT-FOUND honestly recorded rather than fabricated SUPPORTED.');

